  "description": "The first thing that catches your eye when looking at this refrigerator is its large dimensions, more precisely, its high height — 203 cm. This is primarily due to the enlarged refrigerator compartment, which has a volume of 269 liters — while the freezer holds 87 liters (quite decent, but not outstanding score). However, volumes are far from the only feature of the Liebherr CN 4015 refrigerator. So, its main compartment is equipped with a deodorizer and supports fast cooling mode, and the freezer allows you to cool up to 11 kg of food per day to a temperature of -24 °C. The chambers have separate cooling circuits, which allows them to be defrosted individually; however, due to the presence of Full No Frost, this is unlikely to be needed often. Young families will appreciate the 'children's' protection, and in case of a long absence, you can turn on the vacation mode. With all this, the unit belongs to the economical energy class A ++.",
